  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">STRENGTHENING SOCIAL SCIENCES AND HUMANITIES RESEARCH LEADERSHIP CAPACITY AND ECOSYSTEMS IN AFRICA</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">High quality research leadership in social sciences and humanities research, underpinned by 
efficient research ecosystems will play a fundamental role in addressing Africa&#x2019;s sustainable
developmental challenges. This proposed programme of the African Academy of Sciences (The
AAS) builds on the Developing Excellence in Leadership Training and Science in Africa (DELTAS
Africa) programme and integrates key new components informed by The AAS&#x2019;s initiatives in
research management and open access publishing, as well as  community and public
engagement, mentorship and grantsmanship, to strengthen social sciences and humanities
research leadership and social science and humanities research ecosystems in Africa.</narrative>
  </description>
